Week 8 Application Change Log
App Name
Midnight Mixx

Previous Version
My previous Folder Maker App could:

Create a music project folder structure for organizing files.
Create folders for playlists, songs, genres, covers, and project resources.
Save basic project information into text files.
New Version
This version adds:

JSON saving: The application now saves project information into a Project.json file using JSON serialization. The Project class stores information such as project name, current music world, selected mood, playlist name, songs, genre, description, and creation date.

NuGet/package use: The application uses the Newtonsoft.Json NuGet package to serialize and deserialize project information.

File save location: The application now creates the project folder on the user's Desktop using the project name entered in the console. The JSON file is saved inside the Data\JSON folder.

